	<h1 class="title">不管做的是胸罩、蛋糕还是糖，她都想让人脑子里想点什么</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Joshua David Stein</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-28 11:56:36 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19808/medium/19808.png?1451262844" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


